<i>♪ We're doin' it again, yeah ♪</i>

00:38.654 --> 00:40.512
<i>♪ With Webby, his best friend ♪</i>

00:40.599 --> 00:43.611
<i>♪ Do it with Dewey and Webby! ♪</i>

00:50.726 --> 00:51.810
Laddie?

00:51.897 --> 00:53.246
<i>♪ Step, turn, step, turn ♪</i>

00:53.333 --> 00:55.353
